      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start, really sets the mood. can you go a bit deeper into the people hanging out there? maybe describe a couple of specific characters the protagonist might pass by—give me some details on what they look like and what they're doing so i can get a better sense of the crowd.",
      "source": "evaluator"
